nd its 100% secure to apply on our website www.GuaranteedBusinessFunding.org, to get your business funding from our private investor partners from our private American Relief Funding program, please click the link below\r\n www.guaranteedbusinessfunding.org/american-relief-funding.html\r\nIf you have questions during these difficult times for your industry,   please text  Adam at 310-492-3704 (text only 24 hours a day) If you want to call, please call Adam at 310-492-3704 (7 am to 5 PM EST 7 days a week) if you have any questions or email GetApproved@GuaranteedBusinessFunding.org  anytime', '', '', '', 'Botox and Dysport', '[null,null,null]', 0, 0, '2022-01-24');
